00:22:42.590 --> 00:22:45.960
shiroto iwaretara

00:22:45.960 --> 00:22:49.430
ben siyah derim.

00:22:45.960 --> 00:22:49.430
kurodatte icchau

00:22:49.430 --> 00:22:52.890
Kendine karşı dürüst olamayan

00:22:49.430 --> 00:22:52.890
sunaoni narenai

